---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout
  title="Chimney Sweeping Melbourne"
  description="Daves Chimney Sweeping provides local chimney sweeping, flue cleaning and wood heater cleaning across Melbourne and surrounding suburbs. Fast quotes and straightforward service."
  clusterBase="Melbourne"
  clusterRegion="Melbourne and surrounding suburbs"
  homeHref="/"
  servicePageHref="/chimney-sweeping"
  servicePageLabel="Chimney Sweeping"
>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-badge">Local service • Fast quotes • Melbourne suburbs</div>
    <h1>Chimney Sweeping Melbourne</h1>
    <p>
      Daves Chimney Sweeping provides local chimney sweeping, flue cleaning and
      wood heater cleaning across Melbourne and surrounding suburbs.
    </p>
    <p>
      Fast quotes, straightforward service and easy contact for homeowners who
      want their chimney, flue or fireplace cleaned properly.
    </p>

    <div class="button-row">
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/contact">Get a Fast Quote</a>
      <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="tel:0476302729">Call 0476 302 729</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="grid">
    <section class="card">
      <h2>Why Homeowners Choose Us</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Fast quotes with easy contact</li>
        <li>Local service across Melbourne suburbs</li>
        <li>Chimney, flue and wood heater cleaning</li>
        <li>Clear service pages and simple booking process</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="card">
      <h2>What We Help With</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Chimney sweeping</li>
        <li>Flue cleaning</li>
        <li>Wood heater cleaning</li>
        <li>Fireplace cleaning</li>
        <li>Soot and ash buildup removal</li>
        <li>Bird nest and blockage removal</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </div>

  <section class="card">
    <h2>Simple, Straightforward Local Service</h2>
    <p>
      If you need chimney sweeping in Melbourne, the goal is simple. You want a
      local service that is easy to contact, clear about what it does and fast
      to quote.
    </p>
    <p>
      Daves Chimney Sweeping focuses on chimney cleaning, flue cleaning and wood
      heater cleaning for homeowners across Melbourne and surrounding suburbs,
      with a straightforward process from first enquiry through to the job.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="card">
    <h2>Common Reasons People Contact Us</h2>
    <p>
      Many homeowners get in touch before winter, after a season of regular
      fireplace use, or when they notice visible soot buildup, smoke drift,
      unusual smells, reduced airflow or a wood heater that is not drawing
      properly.
    </p>
    <p>
      Keeping your chimney and flue clean can help your fireplace or heater work
      more smoothly and make the setup easier to use through the colder months.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="card">
    <h2>Local Areas We Service</h2>
    <p>
      We provide chimney sweeping services across Melbourne, including Melton,
      Melton South, Melton West, Brookfield, Kurunjang, Harkness, Cobblebank,
      Sunbury, Diggers Rest, Gisborne, Riddells Creek, Bacchus Marsh, Darley,
      Maddingley and Ballan.
    </p>
    <p>
      Looking for a more local page? Visit our
      <a href="/chimney-sweeping/melton">Melton chimney sweeping page</a>,
      <a href="/chimney-sweeping/sunbury">Sunbury chimney sweeping page</a> or
      <a href="/chimney-sweeping/bacchus-marsh">Bacchus Marsh chimney sweeping page</a>.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="card">
    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

    <h3>How often should a chimney be cleaned?</h3>
    <p>
      That depends on how often the fireplace or wood heater is used, but many
      homeowners book chimney sweeping after regular winter use or before the
      colder months start.
    </p>

    <h3>Do you clean wood heater flues as well?</h3>
    <p>
      Yes. We provide flue cleaning and wood heater cleaning as well as general
      chimney sweeping and fireplace cleaning.
    </p>

    <h3>What are common signs a chimney needs cleaning?</h3>
    <p>
      Common signs include visible soot buildup, smoke coming back inside, poor
      draft, unusual smells and reduced airflow.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="card">
    <h2>Request a Quote</h2>
    <p>
      Need chimney sweeping, flue cleaning or wood heater cleaning? Call
      <a href="tel:0476302729">0476 302 729</a> or use our
      <a href="/contact">contact form</a> for a fast quote.
    </p>
  </section>
</MainLayout>